General.Name: Midway Holding AB ser. B
General.Description: Midway Holding AB (publ) offers scaffolding systems and services for complex projects in industry, infrastructure, and construction. It develops and delivers scaffolding systems, weather protection systems, hanging scaffolding, and stamping systems; develops, produces, and markets machine equipment for converting plastic materials to rolled products; and technical solutions, product training, customer support, and financing solutions, as well as provides contract manufacturing for industrial customers. The company also imports and sells grinding and construction machines, lifting equipment, material handling equipment, air cleaners, industrial vacuums cleaners, and twister cleaning systems and lasers to construction industry. Midway Holding AB (publ) was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
